 urnkey solution using SYMKLOUD Converged Platforms. The overall approach e
 nsures service providers and private cloud architects can achieve high-ava
 ilability\, ease of deployment and scaling\, monitoring\, Ironic/Bare-meta
 l\, Ceph\, Kubernetes\, DPDK acceleration\, and SDN and NFV readiness. Fol
 low us on our journey where\, armed with Canonical OpenStack and tools\, a
 utomation\, and Kontron in-house continuous integration and development [C
 I/CD]\, we strove for a uniquely integrated out-of-the-box private cloud s
 olution.
