 re solid technical support to satisfy the demand of digitalization transfo
 rmation. Meanwhile\, China railway infrastructure should support dozens 
 of mission critical applications\, such as passenger transportation\, frei
 ght transportation\, scheduling\, maintenance and public infrastructure pl
 atform.\nBecause of the differences among the application importance\, per
 formance requirements\, fault-tolerant mechanisms\, usage scenarios\, and 
